GENERAL MOTORS CORP; AUTOMOBILES; PRODUCT DEVELOPMENT; SATURN (AUTOMOBILE) 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA111390-0082 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 307301 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
November 13, 1990, Tuesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
