ECONOMY; FINANCIAL PLANNING; RETIREMENT; PENSIONS; INDIVIDUAL RETIREMENT FUNDS; 
SOCIAL SECURITY; DIVORCE; MORTGAGES; EQUITY 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
